					<h4>Western Book Roundup</h4>
		
		<h1>Proulx News, Fuller on Wyoming Oil, and Cather Archive Goes Online</h1>
		<h2><i></i></h2>
		<div class="text-feature_print">
							<p>By Jenny Shank, 4-30-08</p>
			
							<table width="25" align="right" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
					<tr>
						<td>&nbsp;</td>
						<td><img src="http://www.newwest.net/images/thumbnails_feature/alexandrafuller_thumb.jpg" align="right" width="301" height="300" /></td>
